{"tid":1189716,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食物跌落地3秒法則？！醫科教授：可以增強免疫力","createTime":"2019-06-07T02:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T03:58:58.000Z","uid":56881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a227f29c103bb5978d72ed8ea508badc59948302","tid":1189716,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:27:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B03%E7%A7%92%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87-%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E5%8A%9B-%E9%A3%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%A3%9F%E9%9D%9E-122544632.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhktravelnow.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25B7%258C%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%259C%25B03%25E7%25A7%2592%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2589%2587-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%258A%259B-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%259D%259E-122544632.html&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e2bkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=64482cc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hktravelnow.yahoo.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%B7%8C%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B03%E7%A7%92%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87-%E9%86%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88-%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E5%8A%9B-%E9%A3%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%A3%9F%E9%9D%9E-122544632.html</a><br />\n<br />\n進食時偶爾會不慎將食物弄翻，掉到地上，但是坊間都流傳一套「3秒法則」，指食物跌在地上3秒內拾起還能吃，不會沾上細菌。到底這種說法是否準確？最近就有東京醫科榮譽教授撰文，表示跌在地上的食物不但可以拾起來吃，更可以增強免疫力！<br />\n<br />\n撿起來吃 腸道更健康？！<br />\n東京醫科齒科大學榮譽教授，藤田紘一郎先生早前撰文，指出其實腸道菌中最多數量的「日和見菌」，大都是來自外界的土壤微生物菌。而腸道菌群的多樣性對人類健康尤其重要，吸入這種土壤微生物菌能夠提高腸道內的菌群數量和活動力，形成健康腸道，從而增強免疫力。而食物掉在地上，就有可能沾上這種土壤微生物菌！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ff2FXSZwk3zrjBJOE0.NEg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/__831/e7632b155fed6c20107bc814e4e6844d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fff2FXSZwk3zrjBJOE0.NEg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2F__831%2Fe7632b155fed6c20107bc814e4e6844d&h=8d3557c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藤田紘一郎<br />\n東京醫科齒科大學榮譽教授，藤田紘一郎先生，曾經撰寫《88招防癌顧腸術》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.VMDYl8kz92zBUDAwh_ovg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/__831/9b4e283bde08805f0f5e7f32ac75d4fa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.VMDYl8kz92zBUDAwh_ovg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2F__831%2F9b4e283bde08805f0f5e7f32ac75d4fa&h=bbd7b623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日和見菌<br />\n而「日和見菌」不是惡菌也不是益菌，只會根據腸道環境不同，變成多數菌群的那一方（即是若惡菌較多，日和見菌也會變成惡菌）。<br />\n<br />\n為甚麼健康的腸道能夠增強免疫力呢？因為人體70%以上的免疫細胞都在腸道，若是惡菌的數目增多，身體免疫力會下降，從而引致皮膚差以及容易患上感冒，而且一旦增加，就會變成易胖體質，相反地若是減少，就容易瘦下來。<br />\n<br />\n3秒法則 拾食物 掉食物<br />\n原來3秒法則是真的！<br />\n<br />\n英國研究：3秒沒問題 某類食物更可堅持半小時<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》，較早前亦有英國大學測試，把各類食物分別掉到含1,000萬細菌的地毯、瓷磚與普通地板上，發現高鹽、高糖份的食物若掉在地上，只要在5秒內拾起則依然安全，而朱古力、餅乾、三文治等食物更可留在地版上30分鐘而不受細菌污染。研究人員表明，食物只是掉在室內地板幾秒的話，很少機會會接觸到有害的細菌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wksn1gyspc2SYK9BImCLtA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hant/__831/5fdcb00a6946aba62702a78f790f3a4c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWksn1gyspc2SYK9BImCLtA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hant%2F__831%2F5fdcb00a6946aba62702a78f790f3a4c&h=ce2a5815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國大學研究中的部分結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真架"},{"pid":"6fa667e43ff7c22304e90ea77198ecfddc99ac30","tid":1189716,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:28:39.000Z","msg":"英國研究<br />\n中國製造<br />\n香港新聞"},{"pid":"a4641c44f0928d6931f7c9752813accc77f52